stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> FREE

  FREE --> LOADING: reserve frame / register loading
  LOADING --> CLEAN: read ok / publish
  LOADING --> FREE: read failed / cleanup

  FREE --> DIRTY_PENDING: createPage / init new page

  CLEAN --> DIRTY_PENDING: page modified by active MTR
  DIRTY --> DIRTY_PENDING: dirty page modified again

  DIRTY_PENDING --> DIRTY: MTR commit assigns redo LSN
  DIRTY_PENDING --> CLEAN: MTR abort restores clean before image
  DIRTY_PENDING --> DIRTY: MTR abort restores previous dirty image
  DIRTY --> FLUSHING: flush starts
  FLUSHING --> CLEAN: write ok and no newer modification
  FLUSHING --> DIRTY: write ok but modified again
  FLUSHING --> DIRTY: write failed

  CLEAN --> EVICTING: chosen clean victim
  EVICTING --> FREE: remove from hash and reset
  EVICTING --> CLEAN: last check failed

  CLEAN --> STALE: page freed or tablespace dropped
  DIRTY --> STALE: page freed with cleanup policy
  STALE --> EVICTING: bufFixCount becomes zero

  CLEAN --> CLEAN: read hit / LRU update

  note right of LOADING
    ioState=READ or READ_AHEAD
    concurrent misses wait on PageLoadFuture
  end note

  note right of DIRTY
    inFlushList=true
    oldestModificationLsn is stable until clean
  end note

  note right of DIRTY_PENDING
    not in FlushList
    not flushable
    protected by active MTR
  end note

  note right of EVICTING
    requires bufFixCount=0
    requires ioState=NONE
    requires no page latch owner
  end note
